=== RAW MODEL ANSWER ===
Answer: Step 1: Start from methyl 4-ethyl-2-methoxybenzoate; ortho-formylate (s-BuLi/TMEDA, then DMF) to give methyl 3-formyl-4-ethyl-2-methoxybenzoate, then treat with hydrazine to cyclize to 6-ethyl-8-methoxyphthalazin-1(2H)-one | Step 2: Chlorodehydrate the phthalazinone with POCl3 to the electrophile 4-chloro-6-ethyl-8-methoxyphthalazine | Step 3: In parallel, convert N-Boc-4-piperidone-3-carboxylate by Vilsmeier-type formylation/chlorination (DMF/POCl3) to the 4-chloro-5-formyl enone, then condense with hydrazine to form the fused pyrazole tert-butyl 4,5-dihydro-1H-pyrazolo[4,3-c]pyridine-3-carboxylate | Step 4: Hydrolyze the ester to the acid, couple with cyclopropylamine to give the 3-(cyclopropylcarboxamido) fused heterocycle, then remove Boc to furnish 4,5-dihydro-1H-pyrazolo[4,3-c]pyridine-3-carboxamide bearing the free ring NH | Step 5: Displace chloride in 4-chloro-6-ethyl-8-methoxyphthalazine with that deprotected pyrazolo[4,3-c]pyridine amine under SNAr conditions (DIPEA, n-BuOH or DMF, heat) to give CCc1cc2nncc(N3CCc4[nH]nc(C(=O)NC5CC5)c4C3)c2cc1OC.

